sequenceDiagram
  participant FE as Frontend (Vite/React)
  participant API as Backend (Express / Netlify Functions)
  participant AI as Gemini API
  participant DB as Supabase (Postgres)
  participant CACHE as ai_insights_cache

  FE->>API: POST /api/ai/chat or /.netlify/functions/ai-chat
  API->>GEMINI: Request to gemini-2.5-flash (with fallback chain)
  alt Cache hit
    API->>CACHE: Read cached summary (24h)
    CACHE-->>API: Return cached summary
    API-->>FE: 200 OK (cached)
  else Cache miss
    AI->>API: Gemini response
    API->>CACHE: Write summary (user_id+scope)
    API-->>FE: 200 OK (fresh)
  end
  FE->>DB: PostgREST queries (orders/products) for charts
  DB-->>API: Query results
  API-->>FE: Aggregated data + AI insights
